<%# subject: Your portal invitation is expiring soon %>
<div style="<%- S.tagline %>">Portal · Reminder</div>
<h1 style="<%- S.h1 %>">Your invitation expires on <%= euDate(expiresAt) %></h1>
<p style="<%- S.body %>">Hi <%= recipientName %>,</p>
<p style="<%- S.body %>">A quick reminder — your DB Studio portal invitation hasn't been accepted yet, and the link expires on <%= euDate(expiresAt) %>. Once expired, the operator has to reissue it.</p>
<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="<%- S.ctaWrap %>">
  <tr><td style="<%- S.ctaCell %>"><a href="<%= inviteUrl %>" style="<%- S.ctaLink %>">Accept invitation →</a></td></tr>
</table>
<p style="<%- S.note %>">If you're not expecting access to a DB Studio project, you can ignore this email.</p>
